{"tid":1779915,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"We are Hong Kong！香港球迷在東亞杯男足狂噓中国国歌","createTime":"2019-12-12T03:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T04:55:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"08e1d84e3b28b1b34e3c2bd2d0010d76a7d3b16c","tid":1779915,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T03:58:57.000Z","msg":"東亞足球錦標賽11日傍晚在韓國釜山由香港男足出戰地主韓國隊。陸媒環球時報引述香港東網報導，一批前赴觀戰的香港球迷，在賽前狂噓國歌，還呼喊「We are Hong Kong」。<br />\n<br />\n這場比賽結果，香港0-2不敵韓國。雖然輸掉比賽，但引起韓國媒體關注，對香港球迷堅持「We are Hong Kong」的立場進行了即時報導。<br />\n<br />\n環球時報以「暴徒」形容香港球迷，並報導「這並非暴徒第一次在足球賽場上噓國歌。」<br />\n<br />\n環時報導指出，今年11月14日在香港大球場舉行世界盃亞洲區週邊賽第二圈&mdash;中國香港對巴林的比賽，「現場再次出現球迷噓國歌的行為，還有人唱亂港歌曲，喊亂港口號等。」<br />\n<br />\n更早之前的9月10日世界盃預賽亞洲區40強賽第二回合開戰，香港隊在大球場主場迎戰伊朗隊，也有香港球迷在賽前噓國歌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7331/4221653\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7331%2F4221653&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnAN5VMZmAwfp0CD4JwUII9h4%3D&h=1af56e9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7331/4221653</a>"},{"pid":"afaf0898c3ad63b839727d5eb04deadff277c345","tid":1779915,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:50:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ecdb2c0bd6dc7746ad4b4947a367c0def3254e0","tid":1779915,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:51:05.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8d3b62812062d51a6b9ac723b3b263e25e9bdbe7","tid":1779915,"uid":74958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:52:58.000Z","msg":"手足好波"},{"pid":"a443e5ab53173106001e95dce9cf117d7c1aede9","tid":1779915,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s